INSERT Items(ID,Titel,Categorie,Postcode,Locatie,Land,Verkoper,Prijs,Valuta,Conditie,Thumbnail,Beschrijving) VALUES (141475452948,'Renault Clio Grande 1.2 RN 3 door',9861,'GU170EX','Verenigd Koninkrijk','GB','den100967','205.0','GBP','Tweedehands','img141475452948.jpg','<div>Please read! If you bid and win this doesn''t mean you do not turn up or promise to turn up and don''t. I have now had relist again due bidders not attending due to their personal circumstances of how they will travel to pick it up. Please only bid if you have means of getting here in a timely manner. &nbsp;If you have feedback score of less than 10 please phone me first before bidding.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>Sorry to be so blunt. Please read below for the details</div><font face="Arial" size="2"><div><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></div>This is a brilliant little Clio. It''s the Grande model so it comes with power steering, remote central locking and electric windows. I would describe the body work a fair but there is no rust what so ever. Everything on the car is operational and works fine.</font><div><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2">The mileage is high at nearly 126000 but the engine is excellent with no leaks and no blue smoke. It recently had a service including oil and filter, spark plugs and air filter.&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2">It has five good tyres a decent radio and it drives really well. The exhaust was recently replaced and the cambelt looks like new.</font></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2">There is around 6 months MOT left on it. &nbsp; The tax runs out at the end of the month but this is not a issue as the rules have now changed.</font></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2">It will need a new exhaust mount on the rear but is it not dangerous. &nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2">All in all a brilliant little Clio.</font></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2">It being sold with no reserve and a low starting price.</font></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2">If you bid you buy no Walter Mitty''s please and cash only on collection.</font></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial" size="2">For correspondence my number is 07989 745012</font></div>')
