INSERT Items(ID,Titel,Categorie,Postcode,Locatie,Land,Verkoper,Prijs,Valuta,Conditie,Thumbnail,Beschrijving) VALUES (141467374637,'Mitsubishi Delica Space Gear Exceed',18230,'RH12NH','Verenigd Koninkrijk','GB','gazlenbaker','2500.0','GBP','Tweedehands','img141467374637.jpg','The vehicle has been in the UK since 2005 and was first registered in 1994, making it a ''M'' reg. 
It has 7 seats with grey velour trim. The front two and middle two seats have fold up/down armrests. The front two seats are heated for those cold winter days. The middle two seats are swivel base ''captains'' chairs and have both lap and pillar seatbelts that give you plenty of seating options. The rear three seats fold up to give you plenty of space and also fold down giving you a bed and making it into a ''camper''.
The vehicle is 4x4, has dual/twin batteries, factory diff locks, 4 as new tyres fitted and two good spares, alloy wheels, custom stainless steel exhaust system, side steps / running boards, front bullbar, front sunroof, rear moon / sunroof with fully working electric blinds, electric windows, central locking, stereo, rear tailgate mirror and heavy duty tow bar.  There is also a spare injector pump. The heating / cooling and lighting can also be controlled from the rear of the vehicle. An after market fuse box has been professionally fitted.
There are high amp cigarette lighter sockets fitted in the middle and rear of the vehicle for charging accessories whilst on the road.
This is a very versatile vehicle with loads of space and there are not many around. It is, by far, the most practical vehicle we have ever owned and we are only selling it because we are re-locating overseas. It is a great family vehicle and we will be sad to let it go.
The mileage is 136900, but shows on the speedo in kilometres (219000).
Please contact us if you have any questions')
