<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial"><br></font></div>
<div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial"><b>BUY IT NOW:</b></font></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial">There is no buy it now option on our part exchange disposal vehicles, all auctions are no reserve 7-10 day auctions that run until close. Please do not send messages asking to buy these vehicles on a ''buy it now'' or ''cash price'' outside the terms of the auction as such messages will not be responded to. We are fully committed to selling all our part exchanges via ebay auction, and have done since 2007. We never end a listing early, to make it fair to all bidders.<br><br></font><b style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">PART EXCHANGE:</b></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial">We do not take part exchanges against the part exchanges we are selling.<br><br></font></div>
<div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial"><b>ROAD TAX:</b></font></div>
<div><font face="Arial">As of 1st October 2014, DVLA regulations have changed in relation to road tax. Any road tax remaining on a vehicle when owned by the previous keeper is under the new regulations now deemed null and void, and so is no longer transferable. There is however a nearby post office where most winning bidders choose to tax cars on collection. You no longer need to show proof of insurance to do this, but it is your responsibility to ensure the vehicle is insured.</font></div></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial"><br></font></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial"><b>FINAL AUCTION PRICE:</b></font></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial">The amount at which the auction ends, is the final sale price. There will be no negotiation upon this price as you will have had the opportunity to satisfy yourself with the condition of the vehicle before bidding.</font></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial"><br></font></div>
<div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial"><b>PAYMENT:</b></font></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial">Cash</font></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial">Bank Transfer</font></div>
<div><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Debit Card</span></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial"><br><u>We do not accept:</u><br>Credit Card, Business or Personal Cheques,&nbsp;</font><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Bankers Draft/Building Society Cheque</span></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial"><br></font></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial">NB - All funds must be cleared before vehicles will be released. Please settle all payments and collections within 3-5 days of the auction close.&nbsp;</font><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">If vehicles are not paid for within 7 days an unpaid item case is raised and they will be relisted.</span></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial"><br></font></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial"><b>COLLECTION:</b></font></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial">- Please notify us of when you plan to collect, via ebay message so we have it on file, within 24hrs of the end of the auction.</font></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial">- Please pay for and collect all vehicles within 5 days of the end of the auction</font></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial">- We do not deliver<br><br><b>UNPAID ITEMS:</b><br>Sometimes a winning bidder (usually from some distance away) may not make contact, payment or collect a vehicle. In these instances, as per company policy, we will raise an unpaid item case after 5 days, then the vehicle will be relisted in the following weeks auction listings.</font></div></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial"><br></font></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial"><b>COLLECTION HOURS:</b></font></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial">Weekdays - 8:30am - 5:00pm</font></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial">Saturdays - 3:00pm - 5:00pm</font></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial">Sundays - By appointment only</font></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial"><br></font></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial"><b>FEEDBACK:</b></font></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial">Our feedback is important to us and due to time wasters and people not reading the listings properly it takes an unwarranted hit from time to time. We are an up front and honest company. Please be fully aware of what you are buying in the section below.</font></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial"><br></font></div>
<div>
<div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial"><b>UNDERSTAND WHAT YOU ARE BUYING:</b></font></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial">Private buyers should take particular note: We are providing you with accurate information about the physical appearance of the vehicle, together with details of known faults, should the previous owner have passed any on. We are also providing you with an opportunity to inspect the vehicle or have it inspected by professional mechanics, so that you can make an informed decision as to whether a particular vehicle in its current condition will suit your needs. AA/RAC mechanical inspections are welcome.&nbsp;<br></font></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial">- This vehicle has been part exchanged by its previous owner against a new or used car that we have sold them.</font></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial">- This vehicle falls outside of our strict forecourt retail criteria, due to either, or a combination of age, mileage or condition. It has not been mechanically inspected, and so is offered here for ebay auction trade disposal.</font></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial">- The vehicle is in exactly the same condition as when the previous owner part exchanged it. If we are made aware of any existing faults with the vehicle, we ensure we note them in the listing.</font></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial">- We try to ensure we photograph any bodywork damage, but please be aware that we do sometimes unintentionally miss some bits, and on some of the older cars it is hard to document all damage within ebay''s 12 photograph limit, in which case we&nbsp;endeavor&nbsp;to show the most serious damage in the photos attached to the listing.</font></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial">- Please understand that although you are buying a car from a Citroen &amp; Vauxhall Main Dealer, you are getting the opportunity to buy a car at a trade price, in trade condition. By buying direct and cutting out the ''middle man'' you are not only cutting out the retail profit margin of the independent used car trader/dealer, but at the same time you are also cutting out any cosmetic bodywork repairs and mechanical rectification work (if required), that that used car trader/dealer would have provided. We advise all buyers to take the precaution of having the vehicle inspected by their mechanic before putting the vehicle into use.</font></div>
<div><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><font color="#ff0010">By bidding on this auction, you are doing so with the full understanding of the above.</font></span></div></div>
<div><br></div>
<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial"><b>Click&nbsp;</b></font><strong><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial, sans-serif"><a href="http://my.ebay.co.uk/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;mode=0&amp;preference=0&amp;sellerid=pentonmotorgroup&amp;ru=http%3A%2F%2Fcgi.ebay.co.uk%2Fws%2FeBayISAPI.dll%3FViewItem%26item%3D130293270899&amp;ssPageName=STRK:MEFS:ADDVI" target="_blank"><span style="COLOR: rgb(0,44,253)">here</span></a></span></strong><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial"><b>&nbsp;to&nbsp;<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff0010">SUBSCRIBE</font>&nbsp;to our ebay shop email summary of vehicles we list on ebay</b></font></div></div></div></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table><span id="closeHtml"></span></font>')
